{"type":"message","id":"9f0493a6","parentId":"afc7261b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:49:48.666Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yid70c81c5gr_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5684\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=1165\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\n[mutation proposed] a\n[master 4587746] pulse: 2026-03-24 114915\n 6 files changed, 319 insertions(+), 101 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 114915.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 114915.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 114815.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 114915 - The CFI analysis reveals a clear split: 44.8% of invariants are noise (CFI=0) while only 5.7% are true causal anchors (CFI�0.7). The next logical step is implementing a CFI-weighted compression experiment to test whether prioritizing high-CFI tokens improves next-pulse prediction compared to the frequency baseline.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"quick-zephyr","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5684\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=1165\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\n[mutation proposed] a\n[master 4587746] pulse: 2026-03-24 114915\n 6 files changed, 319 insertions(+), 101 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 114915.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 114915.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 114815.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 114915 - The CFI analysis reveals a clear split: 44.8% of invariants are noise (CFI=0) while only 5.7% are true causal anchors (CFI�0.7). The next logical step is implementing a CFI-weighted compression experiment to test whether prioritizing high-CFI tokens improves next-pulse prediction compared to the frequency baseline.\n","name":"powershell Bypass"},"isError